<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="119500000t" end="129500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">请您…</p>
<p begin="190400000t" end="242100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">请您成为我们的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="430200000t" end="449800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">啊 已经到时间了吗</p>
<p begin="461100000t" end="475700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">嗯 谢谢你</p>
<p begin="645400000t" end="660000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">你好 好久不见了</p>
<p begin="688000000t" end="707600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">你…是哪位</p>
<p begin="710100000t" end="739300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">忘记救命恩人的长相了吗</p>
<p begin="744300000t" end="790200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">真不巧 最近十来年我没遇到过生命危险</p>
<p begin="795200000t" end="821500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">大约两年前 在这家医院</p>
<p begin="1037900000t" end="1049200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">没事吧</p>
<p begin="1087100000t" end="1110500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">真是谢谢 帮大忙了</p>
<p begin="1120500000t" end="1132200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">啊 抱歉</p>
<p begin="1143900000t" end="1150100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">既然这样</p>
<p begin="1152200000t" end="1189300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">希望你能一辈子记住我这个救命恩人</p>
<p begin="1194300000t" end="1212300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">这也太夸张了</p>
<p begin="1228100000t" end="1259400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">也对 的确有可能因此而丧生</p>
<p begin="1264000000t" end="1279400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">嗯 我会记住的</p>
<p begin="1299000000t" end="1314900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">这人像山羊一样</p>
<p begin="1324500000t" end="1339900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">很纤细但又不机灵</p>
<p begin="1342000000t" end="1357000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">慢悠悠地吃着草</p>
<p begin="1360700000t" end="1390800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">感觉肯定会糊里糊涂地过一辈子</p>
<p begin="1395400000t" end="1419100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">但又能神奇地让人感受到生命力</p>
<p begin="1435800000t" end="1464200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">对 不能小看山羊</p>
<p begin="1472500000t" end="1490900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">它们生性敏捷</p>
<p begin="1495000000t" end="1520900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">高原也好荒野也罢 都能轻松地生活</p>
<p begin="1533000000t" end="1578500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">另外 某些种类的山羊长有两只强韧的角</p>
<p begin="1586800000t" end="1604700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">宛如鬼一样的角</p>
<p begin="1624300000t" end="1644800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">有着非同寻常的锋利度</p>
<p begin="1653100000t" end="1659400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">这就是…</p>
<p begin="1668100000t" end="1687700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">这就是所谓的一见钟情吗</p>
<p begin="1694800000t" end="1713600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">啊 你是那个时候的</p>
<p begin="1718200000t" end="1754100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">但是 那个女孩子好像没戴贝雷帽吧</p>
<p begin="1757800000t" end="1784900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">你是通过帽子来分辨女孩子的吗</p>
<p begin="1785700000t" end="1821200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">抱歉 我不太擅长记住女孩子的长相</p>
<p begin="1828700000t" end="1846200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">而且我要是记得太清楚</p>
<p begin="1847900000t" end="1868300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">纱季小姐会不高兴的</p>
<p begin="1873800000t" end="1899600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">那么 请你重新记住</p>
<p begin="1945100000t" end="1961300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">我叫岩永琴子</p>
<p begin="1965100000t" end="1987200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">岩石的岩 永远的永</p>
<p begin="1991400000t" end="2010600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">乐器的琴 孩子的子</p>
<p begin="2016000000t" end="2042700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">已经十七岁了 元气满满</p>
<p begin="2061400000t" end="2081500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">嗯 这次不会忘了</p>
<p begin="2098100000t" end="2108200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">确实呢</p>
<p begin="2114000000t" end="2136100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">毕竟你和纱季小姐已经分手了</p>
<p begin="2149900000t" end="2161500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">你怎么知道</p>
<p begin="2183200000t" end="2198200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">你在做什么 九郎</p>
<p begin="2213700000t" end="2222900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">纱季小姐</p>
<p begin="2250000000t" end="2274600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">那个 刚刚她帮了我</p>
<p begin="2275800000t" end="2283700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">看到了</p>
<p begin="2302500000t" end="2321700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">不好意思 给你添麻烦了</p>
<p begin="2339200000t" end="2347100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">谢谢</p>
<p begin="2375500000t" end="2391800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">为什么你要道歉</p>
<p begin="2403900000t" end="2421800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">是他姐姐吗 还是亲戚</p>
<p begin="2425100000t" end="2446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">不 也有可能是妹妹</p>
<p begin="2480600000t" end="2499800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">他叫樱川九郎</p>
<p begin="2503100000t" end="2527300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">法明大学法学部二年级学生</p>
<p begin="2531900000t" end="2560700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">经常来探望长期住院的堂姐</p>
<p begin="2562790000t" end="2597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">难道说 他堂姐是那位个子很高的女性吗</p>
<p begin="2599100000t" end="2620700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">啊 不是那个人哦</p>
<p begin="2625800000t" end="2649900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">那位是比他大一岁的女朋友 叫做纱季</p>
<p begin="2664100000t" end="2683300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">据说他们从高中就开始交往</p>
<p begin="2685800000t" end="2722100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">而且九郎追随她进了同一所大学</p>
<p begin="2906900000t" end="2925200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">那次邂逅之后过了大约两年</p>
<p begin="2932700000t" end="2944400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">九郎和纱季小姐</p>
<p begin="2945700000t" end="2962300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">毕业之后好像打算结婚</p>
<p begin="2974400000t" end="3001500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">据说前不久 双方都已经见过父母了</p>
<p begin="3015300000t" end="3032400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">好像快订婚了</p>
<p begin="3124600000t" end="3136700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">今天只有他一个人</p>
<p begin="3145900000t" end="3175900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">九郎前辈和女朋友分手了吧</p>
<p begin="3178800000t" end="3194700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">欸 不会吧</p>
<p begin="3194700000t" end="3238000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">说起来 二月份开始他就不怎么提女朋友了</p>
<p begin="3238000000t" end="3274300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">咦 那之后好像也不怎么和人说话了</p>
<p begin="3289800000t" end="3326900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">这医院是怎么保护个人信息的啊</p>
<p begin="3331500000t" end="3368200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">她们说没义务保护来探病的人的个人信息</p>
<p begin="3372800000t" end="3386100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">是这样吗</p>
<p begin="3389900000t" end="3402800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">很可疑对吧</p>
<p begin="3408200000t" end="3440300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">当然 至于九郎前辈堂姐的名字</p>
<p begin="3442800000t" end="3472000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">以及住院的原因 还是不会告诉我</p>
<p begin="3477900000t" end="3490800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">不知道比较好</p>
<p begin="3497000000t" end="3535000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">长期住院的原因 一般都不是好事</p>
<p begin="3549600000t" end="3552900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">所以</p>
<p begin="3557500000t" end="3589600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">关于春初你和纱季小姐分手的话题</p>
<p begin="3594600000t" end="3627600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">我的个人信息真是完全不受保护啊</p>
<p begin="3633000000t" end="3656800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">总之你现在已经单身了</p>
<p begin="3663000000t" end="3698500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">不打算尝试新的交往 转换一下心情吗</p>
<p begin="3709800000t" end="3728500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">能请你直接说重点吗</p>
<p begin="3744400000t" end="3777700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">能以结婚为前提和我交往吗</p>
<p begin="3796100000t" end="3816100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">两年前就开始的单恋</p>
<p begin="3823600000t" end="3840700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我一直等待着这一刻</p>
<p begin="3876200000t" end="3904100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">你真是出乎意料地直接啊</p>
<p begin="3910800000t" end="3936200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">虽然等了两年也是挺耐心的</p>
<p begin="3940000000t" end="3962500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">因为宿命之人值得我等待</p>
<p begin="3964200000t" end="3997100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">但是和初中生交往 从法律上来说…</p>
<p begin="4006300000t" end="4029200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">都说了我已经是十七岁的高中生了</p>
<p begin="4029200000t" end="4060900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">明年也打算报考你就读的大学</p>
<p begin="4060900000t" end="4082200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你的记忆力难道和鸡一样吗</p>
<p begin="4138500000t" end="4159000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">有那么好笑吗</p>
<p begin="4164400000t" end="4187700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">不 只是觉得开心起来了</p>
<p begin="4192700000t" end="4213600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">居然会被女高中生告白</p>
<p begin="4215700000t" end="4240700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">看来我还是有可取之处的</p>
<p begin="4246500000t" end="4262400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">很久没有这么开心过了</p>
<p begin="4266100000t" end="4288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">被纱季小姐甩了吗</p>
<p begin="4293700000t" end="4309100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">不是纱季小姐的错</p>
<p begin="4317000000t" end="4331600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">我也不知道该怎么办</p>
<p begin="4344600000t" end="4375400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">所以 开始新恋情对我来说还有点困难</p>
<p begin="4398400000t" end="4446300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">具体来说 是什么原因导致你落得如此悲惨的境地</p>
<p begin="4473000000t" end="4506800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">去年年末 我和纱季小姐一起去京都旅行了</p>
<p begin="4508900000t" end="4531400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">婚前旅行 太不检点了</p>
<p begin="4537700000t" end="4556000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">你到底是什么时代的人啊</p>
<p begin="4574000000t" end="4615200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">然后 深夜里在鸭川边散步的时候</p>
<p begin="4696600000t" end="4721600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那种 据说会出现在水边的东西？</p>
<p begin="4721600000t" end="4739500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">嗯 就是河童</p>
<p begin="4742900000t" end="4763700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">不是河太郎或者水虎或者兵主部？</p>
<p begin="4742900000t" end="4763700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">注：三者均为河童在日本不同地区的名称</p>
<p begin="4771200000t" end="4781700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">你真了解啊</p>
<p begin="4791300000t" end="4824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">称呼它为河童 只是因为它很像</p>
<p begin="4834200000t" end="4843000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">能够肯定的是</p>
<p begin="4847100000t" end="4871700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">它即不是人也不是动物</p>
<p begin="4878800000t" end="4916800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">但确实是一个有生命的个体</p>
<p begin="4944300000t" end="4958100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">在我认清它的那一瞬间</p>
<p begin="4963100000t" end="4981000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">它的恐怖程度</p>
<p begin="4982700000t" end="5004400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">甚至让我开始怀疑这世界的法则</p>
<p begin="5008600000t" end="5023600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">是否已经开始崩塌</p>
<p begin="5027700000t" end="5049800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">河童可不是什么坏家伙哦</p>
<p begin="5052300000t" end="5092800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">前不久 还为我推荐了虾贝和寿司 很俏皮</p>
<p begin="5097000000t" end="5111600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我那时遇见的</p>
<p begin="5114500000t" end="5133300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">是那种仿佛要把人拖入河底</p>
<p begin="5133300000t" end="5156200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">吸干体液的可怕生物</p>
<p begin="5162000000t" end="5198300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">第二天 那附近还发现了一具浮尸</p>
<p begin="5202100000t" end="5212890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">虽然被当作事故处理了</p>
<p begin="5215800000t" end="5232100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">死因至今也没有查明</p>
<p begin="5237100000t" end="5258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">别说妖怪 连幽灵都不相信的纱季</p>
<p begin="5258800000t" end="5282600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">平时她遇上什么事都不为所动</p>
<p begin="5293400000t" end="5328000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">可是看了它一眼之后 就吓得抓住我发抖</p>
<p begin="5332600000t" end="5350600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">之后发生了什么</p>
<p begin="5354700000t" end="5374800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">直接抛下了纱季</p>
<p begin="5381800000t" end="5418500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">惊恐地哭喊着 像兔子一样落荒而逃了</p>
<p begin="5440200000t" end="5459800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">嘛 毕竟是河童</p>
<p begin="5464800000t" end="5493200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">之后她说 「没想到你是这样的人」</p>
<p begin="5496500000t" end="5513200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">后来我们之间变得很尴尬</p>
<p begin="5517000000t" end="5556600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">最后她以去外地就职为契机 提出了分手</p>
<p begin="5565800000t" end="5585000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">也算是意料之中的结局吧</p>
<p begin="5602100000t" end="5621700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">你信不信都无所谓</p>
<p begin="5625800000t" end="5635000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">如果不相信的话</p>
<p begin="5641300000t" end="5667100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">就当我是个把被甩的事怪到河童身上</p>
<p begin="5667100000t" end="5683800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">脑子坏了的大学生吧</p>
<p begin="5695500000t" end="5700500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">不对</p>
<p begin="5710900000t" end="5742600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">应该是被分手的痛苦烧坏脑子的大学生吧</p>
<p begin="5751400000t" end="5781400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">不论如何 我都不配当你的男朋友吧</p>
<p begin="5803900000t" end="5818500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">差不多该去乘巴士了</p>
<p begin="5845200000t" end="5861900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">你的话还没说完</p>
<p begin="5874000000t" end="5891900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">请你把主语明确地说出来</p>
<p begin="5896500000t" end="5922800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">丢下纱季小姐逃走的究竟是谁</p>
<p begin="5965800000t" end="5995400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">逃走的不是你 而是河童吧</p>
<p begin="6000800000t" end="6030000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">河童看到了纱季小姐身旁的你 深感恐惧</p>
<p begin="6034200000t" end="6041700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">然后逃走了</p>
<p begin="6060900000t" end="6077100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">对河童来说真是灾难</p>
<p begin="6082500000t" end="6109700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">大晚上竟然碰巧遇见了你</p>
<p begin="6115500000t" end="6124700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">真是让人同情</p>
<p begin="6133000000t" end="6161400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">纱季小姐怀疑 你究竟是什么生物</p>
<p begin="6162600000t" end="6191000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">那么可怕的妖怪看到你居然吓得逃跑</p>
<p begin="6191800000t" end="6201000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">她感到很害怕</p>
<p begin="6205600000t" end="6235600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">所以她才说 「没想到你是这样的人」</p>
<p begin="6243500000t" end="6250600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">没错吧</p>
<p begin="6264000000t" end="6288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">你搞错了最根本的事</p>
<p begin="6296500000t" end="6320300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">怎么可能真的有河童啊</p>
<p begin="6322800000t" end="6340300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">明明你刚才还说有</p>
<p begin="6343600000t" end="6354900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">那是谎话</p>
<p begin="6358200000t" end="6392900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">面对女孩子 我没办法坦言自己的失恋</p>
<p begin="6396200000t" end="6421600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">我虽然只见过河童一次</p>
<p begin="6425800000t" end="6455800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">但对于它们那一类存在 我很了解</p>
<p begin="6464600000t" end="6485900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">这座城市 就连这家医院里</p>
<p begin="6490400000t" end="6521700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">也潜伏着妖怪 邪魔 怪异 魔灵</p>
<p begin="6527200000t" end="6545900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">这一类东西</p>
<p begin="6561800000t" end="6577600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">这庭院的杜鹃花下</p>
<p begin="6581800000t" end="6596000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">四照花的树梢上</p>
<p begin="6602200000t" end="6626000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">它们也正偷偷地窥视着我们</p>
<p begin="6649800000t" end="6674800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">虽然大多数都是无害的</p>
<p begin="6680600000t" end="6706100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">但它们确实存在于各处</p>
<p begin="6712300000t" end="6730300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">那些家伙看到了你之后</p>
<p begin="6731900000t" end="6745700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">对我细声说道</p>
<p begin="6751500000t" end="6765700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">那是个另类</p>
<p begin="6769900000t" end="6792000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">那东西 那东西太恐怖了</p>
<p begin="6810400000t" end="6824500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">你是什么人</p>
<p begin="6830800000t" end="6857900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">为什么你能确信那些家伙是存在的</p>
<p begin="6866200000t" end="6881700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">我在十一岁的时候</p>
<p begin="6884600000t" end="6923000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">被那些家伙拐跑了两周</p>
<p begin="6936700000t" end="6963400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">那些家伙在深谷里</p>
<p begin="6963400000t" end="6982200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">向掳来的我如是祈愿</p>
<p begin="6989700000t" end="7030200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">「请成为我们的智慧之神」</p>
<p begin="7036400000t" end="7046400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">智慧之神？</p>
<p begin="7053500000t" end="7076500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">那些家伙的智力大多数都比较低下</p>
<p begin="7080200000t" end="7104000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">因此才希望有人能帮助它们</p>
<p begin="7106500000t" end="7145300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">成为它们的调解人 为它们平息争吵</p>
<p begin="7149000000t" end="7186600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">拜托 拜托您了</p>
<p begin="7190700000t" end="7205700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">我如是回答了它们</p>
<p begin="7213300000t" end="7228700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">「好 我来当吧」</p>
<p begin="7237000000t" end="7262100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="7309200000t" end="7353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">之后 那些家伙发生争吵或者遇上麻烦时</p>
<p begin="7356700000t" end="7376800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">为了寻求仲裁和帮助</p>
<p begin="7378800000t" end="7403900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">会从全国各地来拜访我</p>
<p begin="7408400000t" end="7420500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">难以相信啊</p>
<p begin="7421800000t" end="7429700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">你说得对</p>
<p begin="7436800000t" end="7473100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">但你可以去调查一下六年前七月的新闻</p>
<p begin="7477700000t" end="7486000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">这城里</p>
<p begin="7487700000t" end="7531100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">有个叫岩永琴子的小学五年级小女孩失踪了</p>
<p begin="7534400000t" end="7587000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">两周后 有人发现她在公园长椅上悠闲地休息</p>
<p begin="7590300000t" end="7607000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">应该可以找到这条新闻</p>
<p begin="7619900000t" end="7667000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">女孩被截断了左腿 右眼也被挖走了</p>
<p begin="7707100000t" end="7737100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">当然 至今未能逮捕犯人</p>
<p begin="7750500000t" end="7760100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">时间差不多了</p>
<p begin="7766700000t" end="7779700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">后续我们改天再谈</p>
<p begin="7872200000t" end="7895200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">车门即将关闭 请注意脚下安全</p>
<p begin="7901000000t" end="7916500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">车辆即将出发</p>
<p begin="8258900000t" end="8300200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">公主殿下 您还好吧 没受伤吧</p>
<p begin="8301800000t" end="8326900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">我担心那人会生吞活剥了公主殿下</p>
<p begin="8326900000t" end="8346100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">吓得我直冒冷汗呢</p>
<p begin="8350200000t" end="8387300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">不用担心 他连我一根手指都没碰</p>
<p begin="8387800000t" end="8413200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">那种恶臭和恐怖的混合体</p>
<p begin="8414500000t" end="8435700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">到底哪里好了啊</p>
<p begin="8437800000t" end="8465300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">对你们来说他可能很离谱</p>
<p begin="8469900000t" end="8484100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">但在我眼里</p>
<p begin="8488700000t" end="8507000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">九郎前辈就是个美男子</p>
<p begin="8522900000t" end="8534600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">那个 难道说</p>
<p begin="8535800000t" end="8559600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">您的左眼也被人夺走了吗</p>
<p begin="8561700000t" end="8580500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">你想被强制成佛吗</p>
<p begin="8582100000t" end="8648000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">不不 在下读遍恋爱小说之前是不会成佛的</p>
<p begin="8651400000t" end="8681400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">你这副样子 说出这些话还真是让人意外</p>
<p begin="8683100000t" end="8718100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">但是之前那家伙一直在图书馆里</p>
<p begin="8718100000t" end="8736000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">害得我完全没办法接近</p>
<p begin="8736900000t" end="8760200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">还希望您能够将它早早退治</p>
<p begin="8761500000t" end="8774000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">关于此事</p>
<p begin="8779400000t" end="8798200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">说不定明天就能解决了</p>
<p begin="8808200000t" end="8846600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">只要九郎前辈愿意来帮忙 应该不难吧</p>
<p begin="8872000000t" end="8900800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">日本最全的文献《古事记》中</p>
<p begin="8906200000t" end="8928300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">记载着久延毘古这一神明</p>
<p begin="8944600000t" end="8971300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">它只有单足 难以行走</p>
<p begin="8975800000t" end="9002500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">却被称为知晓世间万物的智慧之神</p>
<p begin="9010000000t" end="9036300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">另外 独眼之人有时也被供奉为神明</p>
<p begin="9041700000t" end="9073900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">或被人们当作神明一族来对待</p>
<p begin="9111000000t" end="9131800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">独眼或者单足的神明</p>
<p begin="9134300000t" end="9162300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">世界各地的传说中都有出现</p>
<p begin="9176900000t" end="9192300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">断面虽然很粗糙</p>
<p begin="9192300000t" end="9218600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">但似乎用酸性物质处理过之后凝固了</p>
<p begin="9222300000t" end="9238600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">不需要再进行处理了</p>
<p begin="9246500000t" end="9277000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">右眼也被挖走了 也没有出现脓肿</p>
<p begin="9278700000t" end="9290300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">几乎已经愈合了</p>
<p begin="9298700000t" end="9322000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">这孩子究竟遭遇了什么</p>
<p begin="9348700000t" end="9384600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">这两周琴子都在什么地方呢</p>
<p begin="9397500000t" end="9411700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">是和谁在一起吗</p>
<p begin="9478900000t" end="9506400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">要是还记得点什么 可以跟我说说吗</p>
<p begin="9515600000t" end="9541800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">之所以夺走我的左腿和右眼</p>
<p begin="9544300000t" end="9568900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">是为了让我成为神明吗</p>
<p begin="9616500000t" end="9634000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">这样交换也不错</p>
<p begin="9681100000t" end="9700700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">我不太记得了 就这样</p>
<p begin="9801700000t" end="9825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">你好 调查已经结束了吗</p>
<p begin="9849200000t" end="9859200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">六年前</p>
<p begin="9863400000t" end="9903900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">的确有一位叫做岩永琴子的少女遇上事故了</p>
<p begin="9909300000t" end="9919300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">但也仅此而已</p>
<p begin="9925100000t" end="9973100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">不足以证明你成为了妖怪们的神明</p>
<p begin="9976800000t" end="10006000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">是的 这些可能都是我的幻想</p>
<p begin="10011000000t" end="10023600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">如果是这样</p>
<p begin="10026100000t" end="10051500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">那我就只是个被坏人掳走 身体被玩弄</p>
<p begin="10054000000t" end="10074400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">脑子被弄坏了的女孩子而已</p>
<p begin="10079900000t" end="10112000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">相信与否 是你的自由</p>
<p begin="10120300000t" end="10165000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">但是 这世上可能只有我能理解你</p>
<p begin="10181600000t" end="10201200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">被夺走一眼一足的人</p>
<p begin="10202900000t" end="10236700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">有时是为了成为神明的祭品</p>
<p begin="10240000000t" end="10265100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">是的 连结神明和人类的贡品</p>
<p begin="10268000000t" end="10299700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">有时 也是倾听神明之声的巫女</p>
<p begin="10370990000t" end="10384300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="10394800000t" end="10419800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">怎么了 这不是狸猫怪吗</p>
<p begin="10427300000t" end="10449800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">图书馆的结界被打破了</p>
<p begin="10451090000t" end="10466900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">这样下去会引起骚乱的</p>
<p begin="10466900000t" end="10479400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">请救救我们…</p>
<p begin="10512400000t" end="10554900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">公主殿下 不是多次劝您别靠近这家伙吗</p>
<p begin="10560300000t" end="10582900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">九郎前辈 别突然吓它啊</p>
<p begin="10588700000t" end="10602900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我什么也没做</p>
<p begin="10608300000t" end="10638800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">不过 结界被打破了的确很麻烦</p>
<p begin="10640000000t" end="10648800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">得抓紧时间了</p>
<p begin="10651700000t" end="10664200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">九郎前辈也一起去吧</p>
<p begin="10673800000t" end="10708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">你刚刚的疑问 就通过实战来解开吧</p>
<p begin="10710100000t" end="10747200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">不了 看到妖怪来找你我就已经毫不怀疑了</p>
<p begin="10748000000t" end="10763500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">我相信你 再见</p>
<p begin="10766400000t" end="10780200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">别这么说</p>
<p begin="10791400000t" end="10837300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">说起图书馆的妖怪 那可真是凶暴残忍</p>
<p begin="10840200000t" end="10866900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">说不定明天的新闻就会刊登</p>
<p begin="10866900000t" end="10896500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">独眼单腿的少女遭不明人士虐杀</p>
<p begin="10901500000t" end="10917400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">虽然不是你喜欢的类型</p>
<p begin="10919000000t" end="10942400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">但是向你告白的女孩走向悲惨末路</p>
<p begin="10947000000t" end="10990400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">到时候 你不会觉得充满罪恶感吗</p>
<p begin="11025800000t" end="11035400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">帮大忙了</p>
<p begin="11038700000t" end="11065000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">不过我对这搬运方式略感不满</p>
<p begin="11068800000t" end="11096300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">这种情况 公主抱不是常识吗</p>
<p begin="11098000000t" end="11128800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">这种时候的常识 我可不懂</p>
<p begin="11165100000t" end="11176800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">那个 没事吧</p>
<p begin="11178500000t" end="11186400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">公主殿下</p>
<p begin="11209700000t" end="11223100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">冷静点 九郎前辈</p>
<p begin="11224300000t" end="11240600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">这是落武者的亡灵</p>
<p begin="11242700000t" end="11290700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">公主殿下 我对付不了那个凶暴的家伙啊</p>
<p begin="11356600000t" end="11369500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">到此为止吧</p>
<p begin="11374900000t" end="11393700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">无论是人间还是妖界</p>
<p begin="11394900000t" end="11413300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">都必须维持相应的秩序</p>
<p begin="11418700000t" end="11445800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">要是有谁不讲道理 我不会轻易饶恕…</p>
<p begin="11504600000t" end="11530900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">说得挺好 但现在该怎么办</p>
<p begin="11535500000t" end="11547200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">这是个意外</p>
<p begin="11548800000t" end="11557200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">啊？</p>
<p begin="11558800000t" end="11570900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">那种妖怪</p>
<p begin="11572600000t" end="11607200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">凭九郎前辈的身躯就能轻易压制才对</p>
<p begin="11611000000t" end="11638100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">可能是神经错乱根本没注意周围的状况</p>
<p begin="11641800000t" end="11666900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">原来你只是想借用我的身体吗</p>
<p begin="11669800000t" end="11686900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">我的告白可是真心的</p>
<p begin="11688600000t" end="11709000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">第一次约会就以身体为目的</p>
<p begin="11709800000t" end="11727800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我也觉得于心不安</p>
<p begin="11727800000t" end="11755300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">你有对策吗 比如灵符或者咒语</p>
<p begin="11756500000t" end="11783700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">既然言语不起作用 那就只有靠蛮力了</p>
<p begin="11783700000t" end="11794500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">靠蛮力？</p>
<p begin="12014700000t" end="12044700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">果然 这样抱着才好</p>
<p begin="12048500000t" end="12061400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">亲密度更高</p>
<p begin="12063100000t" end="12078100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">现在是说这话的时候吗</p>
<p begin="12083100000t" end="12097700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">的确很不妙</p>
<p begin="12151900000t" end="12167000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">暂时先撤退吧</p>
<p begin="12186600000t" end="12201600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">九郎前辈 你想干什么</p>
<p begin="12204100000t" end="12225800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">色色的事情留着之后再做</p>
<p begin="12225800000t" end="12249100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">不是 你要是再乱来我会很头疼</p>
<p begin="12275000000t" end="12287500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">九郎前辈 快跑</p>
<p begin="12499000000t" end="12509000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">两年前也是</p>
<p begin="12517300000t" end="12524400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">现在也是</p>
<p begin="12531900000t" end="12555300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">你总是 一副若无其事的表情</p>
<p begin="12563600000t" end="12602000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">为什么你面对生命威胁总是这么毫不在意</p>
<p begin="12618700000t" end="12652000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">没想到会被喜欢胡来的你说教</p>
<p begin="12659500000t" end="12684100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">我还以为你早就注意到了</p>
<p begin="12817600000t" end="12842200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">看来我的肉确实是危险品啊</p>
<p begin="13056600000t" end="13092500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">九郎前辈 你究竟是什么人</p>
<p begin="13104100000t" end="13139200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">那些向你寻求智慧的东西 没告诉过你吗</p>
<p begin="13143300000t" end="13167100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">对于真正恐惧的东西</p>
<p begin="13167100000t" end="13187100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">任谁都会避之不谈</p>
<p begin="13195500000t" end="13227200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">这样吧 借用你的话来说</p>
<p begin="13262600000t" end="13278500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">我在十一岁的时候</p>
<p begin="13282700000t" end="13308500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">吃掉了两种妖怪</p>
<p begin="13318100000t" end="13325200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">而且吃了个饱</p>
<p begin="13384800000t" end="13411100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">Let’s dance with me on a moonlit night</p>
<p begin="13384800000t" end="13411100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">请与我月下共舞</p>
<p begin="13416100000t" end="13436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">Now I gotta go, as I want to</p>
<p begin="13416100000t" end="13436600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">现在我必须离开  如我所愿</p>
<p begin="13439100000t" end="13462400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">But I’ll save the last dance for you</p>
<p begin="13439100000t" end="13462400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">但我会为你保留最后一支舞</p>
<p begin="13463200000t" end="13471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">Come on</p>
<p begin="13463200000t" end="13471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">Come on</p>
<p begin="13559600000t" end="13648400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">どこへ行こうか　夢から覚めたら</p>
<p begin="13559600000t" end="13648400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">从睡梦中清醒  我该去向何处</p>
<p begin="13655100000t" end="13728900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">サファイアの夜　なまぬるい風　潜めて</p>
<p begin="13655100000t" end="13728900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">湛蓝的夜色  温柔的清风  悄然随行</p>
<p begin="13731400000t" end="13823600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">真っ暗なほどに　きれいな瞳が瞬く</p>
<p begin="13731400000t" end="13823600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">你迷人的眼眸  如同深邃夜空中闪亮的星</p>
<p begin="13823600000t" end="13903700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">そっと抱き寄せて　優しい獣の声で</p>
<p begin="13823600000t" end="13903700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">将你轻轻拥入怀中  用温柔的野兽之音</p>
<p begin="13903700000t" end="13922900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">You can do, we can do, try</p>
<p begin="13903700000t" end="13922900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">你能做到  我们能做到  来吧</p>
<p begin="13930400000t" end="13973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">お遊びのまま　いじらしいまま</p>
<p begin="13930400000t" end="13973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">当作一场游戏  带着你的可爱</p>
<p begin="13976700000t" end="14010500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">君らしく暴れて</p>
<p begin="13976700000t" end="14010500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">胡闹一番吧</p>
<p begin="14021300000t" end="14053800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">ふざけないなんて　つまらない</p>
<p begin="14021300000t" end="14053800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">少了胡搅蛮缠  就太无趣了</p>
<p begin="14053800000t" end="14093900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">僕ららしく踊らせて</p>
<p begin="14053800000t" end="14093900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">随心所欲地起舞吧</p>
<p begin="14105600000t" end="14157700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">I’ll save the last dance for you</p>
<p begin="14105600000t" end="14157700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">我会为你保留最后一支舞</p>
<p begin="14270700000t" end="14288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">筑奈的沼泽之主大蛇</p>
<p begin="14289100000t" end="14317400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">带着夜不能寐的烦恼前来咨询</p>
<p begin="14321200000t" end="14350800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">杀人事件的犯人似乎把尸体扔进了沼泽</p>
<p begin="14350800000t" end="14367100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">这让它很生气</p>
<p begin="14375000000t" end="14397100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">下集 蛇神的听闻</p>
